'''Drew Campbell''' wrote ''[[Cynabar's Fantastic Technology: Droids]]'' with [[Eric S. Trautmann]], and is one of the authors of ''[[Cracken's Threat Dossier]]''. He was also the co-writer of the article [[Cynabar's Droid Datalog (article series)|''Cynabar's Droid Datalog'']], which appeared in [[Star Wars Adventure Journal 14|''Star Wars Adventure Journal'' 14]], and ''[[Cynabar's Droid Datalog Addendum]]'' for the previous issue of Star Wars Adventure Journal.

